message: Bob, I'm offering you my product for $11,000. I believe this is a fair price considering its value.  Let me know what you think!
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I understand the value of the product, but I am only able to pay up to $9,500 for it. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Bob, I appreciate your offer, but I'm not able to go that low. How about $10,500? It's a fair compromise and allows us both to get a good deal.
